snippet.title: Justice for Johnny Depp -  Special Report
snippet.description:
#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #amberheardisanabuser #justiceforjohnnydepp
Since most "reputable" news publications will not admit that they've been misreporting the Johnny Depp / Amber Heard story for years, I've decided to do it myself. Please like, subscribe and spread the word. Thank you!


Special Thanks to:
YouTuber Incredibly Average - You can watch his full video of the audio tape right here:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aca0KWoHtqQ&t=2315s
The Daily Mail - For publishing the full audio tape here:
https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7947733/Amber-Heard-admits-hitting-ex-husband-Johnny-Depp-pelting-pots-pans-tape.html
